Class _Testbed

  • java.lang.Object
    • _Testbed

  • public class _Testbed
extends java.lang.Object
    This class instantiates shapes objects with four private instance variables. It contains mutator methods to calculate the area of a triangle and the hypotenuse of a triangle. There are getter methods for each private instance variable. Private instance variables include mySide1, mySide2, myArea, and myHypotenuse.
    Version:
    06/08/17
    Author:
